 <item> <title>Education, Justice Departments to Announce New Guidance on the Rights of English Language Learners in Schools</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/media-advisories/education-justice-departments-announce-new-guidance-rights-english-language-learners-schools</link>
 <description>The Departments of Education and Justice will hold a press call at 10:30 a.m. ET on Wednesday to announce new guidance for school districts on the rights of English language learners.

Note:
Press inquiries regarding logistics should be directed to the Justice Department&#039;s Office of Public Affairs at 202-514-2007. </description>
